# REST routing(REST)

# Albums resource

## List all albums
```
GET /albums

Response (200 OK):
A list of albums
```


## Find a specific album
GET /albums/:id

Response(200 OK):
A specific album

## Create a new album

Request:
POST /albums

With body parameters:
  title = 'OK Computer'
  release_year = '1997'
  artist_id = "5"

Response (200 OK):
No content, just creates the new resource (the new album)